22:45.697 --> 22:47.157
You know I'm Ye-sol's father.

22:50.660 --> 22:53.288
You're an even bigger son of a bitch
than I thought you were.

22:54.831 --> 22:56.666
I'm warning you, back off.

22:57.667 --> 22:59.920
This fucking asshole.

23:02.130 --> 23:05.133
- You shouldn't do this here!
- We're outside a police station!

23:05.133 --> 23:06.051
