24:12.909 --> 24:14.077
Shit.

24:17.456 --> 24:18.832
The police said what?

24:18.832 --> 24:21.251
They received a report about the hospital?

24:21.251 --> 24:23.837
Yes, for illegal storage of a corpse.

24:23.837 --> 24:27.340
They want to search the morgue
and the freezer. What should we do?

24:31.011 --> 24:32.262
Where's the body now?

24:34.264 --> 24:37.184
