24:38.101 --> 24:41.271
If we don't do anything with her body,
the corpse will rot.

24:41.271 --> 24:43.273
You have to have a funeral for her.

24:43.273 --> 24:45.859
EVERYTHING WILL BE OVER
IF WE HOLD THE FUNERAL

24:45.859 --> 24:48.111
IT'S UNFAIR, SO UNFAIR

24:48.945 --> 24:51.948
PLEASE, HELP ME

24:51.948 --> 24:53.533
PLEASE

24:53.533 --> 24:55.076
PLEASE HELP
MY POOR DAUGHTER, DOCTOR

24:55.076 --> 24:56.745
Doing this here won't help you!

24:57.704 --> 25:00.665
I need to know
you understand what I'm telling you.

25:00.665 --> 25:03.168
AGREEMENT TO HOLD FUNERAL

25:03.168 --> 25:04.961
Please review this, and then sign.

25:04.961 --> 25:07.380
You can sign with a thumbprint.

25:11.593 --> 25:13.261
Please, ma'am! You have to sign.

25:15.222 --> 25:18.391
This whole thing is tragic.
Without the family's consent,

25:18.391 --> 25:20.810
