26:28.503 --> 26:31.506
Hard to say, but we're obligated
to investigate this case.

26:32.090 --> 26:35.385
I need the body moved back to the morgue.

26:36.636 --> 26:39.014
I filed the report.
Understand what I'm saying?

26:40.682 --> 26:41.600
Yeah.

26:42.517 --> 26:45.645
So you admit that the hospital moved
the body from the morgue to the freezer,

26:45.645 --> 26:46.896
