and went to her grandmother's.

28:54.858 --> 28:56.443
Mr. Ha is inside, ma'am.

29:04.409 --> 29:06.619
<i>I requested
a temporary restraining order</i>

29:06.619 --> 29:07.829
<i>against Mr. Jeon Jae-jun.</i>

29:07.829 --> 29:09.497
<i>We'll proceed as quickly as we can.</i>

29:10.331 --> 29:11.332
I see, good work.

29:11.332 --> 29:13.835
