I'll see you at the office tomorrow.

29:13.835 --> 29:16.004
Why did you send Ye-sol to your mother's?

29:16.004 --> 29:18.131
I have my reasons. We'll talk later.

29:18.131 --> 29:19.966
I have to hear it from the drive...

29:21.092 --> 29:21.926
What happened?

29:23.762 --> 29:24.846
A fight?

29:24.846 --> 29:26.389
I don't think we should talk now,

29:26.389 --> 29:28.349
