you truly care about is yourself.

30:30.954 --> 30:32.705
Ye-sol is suffering...

30:35.625 --> 30:37.544
and you want to argue with me?

30:40.046 --> 30:41.047
At least...

30:42.882 --> 30:44.551
I tried to protect us

30:45.635 --> 30:46.886
with these secrets.

30:48.429 --> 30:50.932
You destroyed it by dragging it all out.

30:50.932 --> 30:52.851
What did you want to protect?

30:53.977 --> 30:56.646
Our marriage, your career,
Ye-sol, your lover?

30:59.232 --> 31:01.067
You couldn't protect any of it.

31:07.156 --> 31:08.908
Let me make this very clear.

31:11.661 --> 31:13.079
Ye-sol's mine...

31:15.874 --> 31:17.292
even if you're not.

31:40.565 --> 31:42.650
SEUNG-A'S MOM

31:44.444 --> 31:45.278
How are you, girl?

31:45.278 --> 31:47.196
<i>Why aren't you answering my texts?</i>

31:47.196 --> 31:49.532
<i>What do you think
about this whole bribery thing?</i>

31:49.532 --> 31:51.284
<i>We're headed to the school now.</i>

31:51.284 --> 31:53.036
<i>You coming? We need your vote?</i>

31:53.036 --> 31:54.829
<i>It's a total mess over there!</i>

31:54.829 --> 31:57.040
<i>Also, did you hear
one of the teachers got arrested?</i>

31:57.040 --> 31:58.541
<i>Isn't that crazy?</i>

31:58.541 --> 32:00.376
Oh, I'm sorry I didn't text.

32:01.085 --> 32:02.712
I'm at work right now.

32:03.296 --> 32:04.881
Can you actually vote on my behalf?

32:06.549 --> 32:08.885
Bribes, huh? That's insane.

32:09.886 --> 32:11.721
A teacher like that should be fired.

32:59.435 --> 33:02.105
FROM KIM SI-U'S MOM

33:15.660 --> 33:18.621
What are you doing? You should have
let me know you were coming.

33:18.621 --> 33:21.708
Leave these alone.
I haven't taken the tags off yet.

33:22.583 --> 33:23.710
Get off!

33:24.419 --> 33:26.045
Hey! Hey!

33:26.045 --> 33:27.130
Stop!

33:30.967 --> 33:33.386
That was the last thing
you should've done to me.

33:33.886 --> 33:35.805
You can track me down here and show up

33:35.805 --> 33:38.641
and invade my life
like the shameless bitch you are,

33:38.641 --> 33:40.059
but the one thing you shouldn't have done

33:40.059 --> 33:42.478
is side with the monster
who ruined my life!

33:44.564 --> 33:46.107
How could you do this again?

33:47.442 --> 33:49.861
How could you abandon me like this again?

33:50.528 --> 33:51.612
It was the one thing...

33:53.656 --> 33:56.534
the one thing
that you never, ever should have done!

33:57.118 --> 34:00.621
Do you even know how much these are worth?

34:08.254 --> 34:09.255
Hey!

34:11.299 --> 34:12.133
Don't do that!

34:12.717 --> 34:13.551
Stop it!

34:14.135 --> 34:15.553
Fuck! Stupid!

34:19.515 --> 34:20.558
Hey,

34:20.558 --> 34:21.768
you crazy bitch!

35:43.349 --> 35:44.976
Hey, what are you doing?

35:46.561 --> 35:47.562
Come out.

35:48.271 --> 35:50.439
Let's have a parent-teacher conference.

35:52.817 --> 35:54.777
I saw Ha Do-yeong at the police station.

35:56.279 --> 35:59.615
Thought I was the only one you told.
Are you two-timing me or what?

36:01.450 --> 36:02.869
Get out of the car, bitch!

36:06.080 --> 36:08.958
Whoa! Whoa!

36:10.459 --> 36:11.586
Yeah, go on.

36:12.545 --> 36:13.546
Hit me!

36:14.255 --> 36:16.924
Go on and hit me,
you fucking loser!

36:28.311 --> 36:29.145
Are you okay?

36:33.858 --> 36:36.944
Oh man, I just recently got this car.

36:36.944 --> 36:39.363
I'm still adjusting to it.
Did you get hurt?

36:42.241 --> 36:44.952
Oh my God, it's this asshole.
Fucking crazy.

36:48.789 --> 36:49.790
Are you drunk?

36:49.790 --> 36:53.085
Why'd you stand in front of someone's car
in the pouring rain?

36:53.085 --> 36:54.670
And dressed in all black.

36:55.171 --> 36:57.757
If it weren't for my high-performance car,
I could've hit you.

36:58.925 --> 37:02.470
Man, be more careful next time.
You don't wanna die, right?

37:03.095 --> 37:03.930
What?

37:04.513 --> 37:05.681
Jesus Christ.

37:06.641 --> 37:07.975
You're a fucking psycho.

37:09.018 --> 37:10.519
Here, this is my card.

37:12.855 --> 37:15.650
Now you know how to reach out
if you need anything from me, right?

37:17.068 --> 37:18.402
I'm a bit busy right now.

37:25.159 --> 37:26.661
