37:28.120 --> 37:30.122
If you keep standing there,
I will hit you this time!

37:36.462 --> 37:39.465
Whoa, whoa! Hey! Stop! Hey!

37:39.465 --> 37:40.633
Hey! Hey! Stop! Shit.

37:42.051 --> 37:43.219
Get out of the car.

37:43.844 --> 37:44.804
Get out, asshole!

37:52.395 --> 37:53.479
Hey.

37:54.647 --> 37:55.564
Hey.

37:56.148 --> 37:56.983
Hey!

38:00.820 --> 38:02.905
Shit. What the fuck is wrong with him?

38:09.620 --> 38:13.499
I'm gonna give up my lease.
You have one week to vacate it.

38:14.834 --> 38:16.168
I hope that today

38:17.712 --> 38:20.589
