ever see each other again.

38:21.674 --> 38:24.760
Stop giving me all this crap
and get out of here.

38:26.262 --> 38:28.764
How many times do I have to tell you?

38:28.764 --> 38:30.599
Blood is thicker than water.

38:30.599 --> 38:32.560
Dong-eun, you remember that.

38:35.187 --> 38:37.606
I just need
a sub-document from the county,

38:37.606 --> 38:41.319
and it'll tell me right where you are.

38:46.949 --> 38:48.451
Go on. Run then.

38:50.453 --> 38:53.914
Let's see if you can hide,
or if I find you.

39:20.858 --> 39:21.859
I'm okay in here.

39:21.859 --> 39:22.943
You?

39:26.614 --> 39:28.115
That's good. I'm okay too.

39:29.533 --> 39:31.619
What are you up to out there right now?

39:32.328 --> 39:33.371
You know.

39:35.498 --> 39:39.168
Just trying to show you I'm here.

39:40.669 --> 39:41.754
Was it obvious?

39:49.845 --> 39:52.681
Can I ask, how did you find me out there?

39:56.811 --> 39:59.980
Your mother reached out to me.
She found my phone number.

40:01.190 --> 40:03.359
Park Yeon-jin must have given it to her.

40:08.864 --> 40:10.199
Well, just so you know,

40:11.033 --> 40:12.284
I'm sleeping in,

40:13.035 --> 40:15.621
and I also plan to sleep early tonight.

40:18.958 --> 40:20.292
So just get some rest.

40:23.295 --> 40:24.922
Good night, then.

40:30.386 --> 40:31.387
Good night.

40:59.331 --> 41:00.666
WHERE'S YOUR CLINIC?
I CAN COME TO YOU

41:00.666 --> 41:01.584
I HEARD YOU'RE A DOCTOR

41:01.584 --> 41:03.127
