if God's even listening right now?

42:02.853 --> 42:04.021
Hey, lady!

42:05.439 --> 42:06.941
So why should I care?

42:07.525 --> 42:10.861
Well, ma'am, the church she's at right now

42:11.737 --> 42:15.491
