by the parents of your friend, you know?

42:32.758 --> 42:35.386
I INVITE YOU
TO THE GARDEN OF EDEN, SISTER

42:59.326 --> 43:00.661
SHEEP HERD OF SUNGHAN CHURCH

43:00.661 --> 43:02.580
SURPRISE SHOW
AT THE UNDERGROUND CHAPEL

43:05.583 --> 43:07.751
YOU'RE ON CAMERA
