how you crawled like an animal.

45:54.835 --> 45:55.836
I remember.

46:00.090 --> 46:01.884
I remember it now.

47:20.546 --> 47:21.630
Was it you?

47:23.131 --> 47:23.966
You did this?

47:25.592 --> 47:28.512
