47:33.892 --> 47:36.186
Sa-ra's only a first-time offender.

47:36.186 --> 47:37.563
She'll get out soon.

47:38.772 --> 47:40.357
You won't bring us down.

47:41.066 --> 47:41.900
Really?

47:42.734 --> 47:45.737
You're gonna try your best
to not get brought down,

47:46.613 --> 47:48.448
Weather Forecaster A.

47:53.996 --> 47:58.000
EXPOSING WEATHER FORECASTER A
FOR SCHOOL VIOLENCE

48:29.156 --> 48:31.116
HTN COLLEAGUES GROUP CHAT
SAW THE SCHOOL VIOLENCE ARTICLE

48:31.116 --> 48:32.200
DRUGS?
FORECASTER WHO?

48:32.200 --> 48:33.118
PROBABLY DRUGS CRAZY

48:41.209 --> 48:42.961
Bitch, what the fuck have you done?

48:44.212 --> 48:47.049
